Package: webportal
Title: Access the Aquatic Informatics WebPortal API from R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Law", , "jason.law@portlandoregon.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The webportal package provides a wrapper for the Aquatic Informatics Web Portal API. Accessing the API requires that you have an account with privileges to access the API for deployed Web Portal. Speak to an administrator for the Web Portal server that you’re interested in if you don’t have these.
